    a responsive countdown time with the setting to pick a date (DD: HH: MM: SS) , make the font JUST SANS it is my theme font, also the text should in line with the countdown (horizontally next to each other) right now it is vertically stacked. height of the section should be only as big as the maqruee section on top. there is no need of the titles below the numbers "DAY" HOURS" etc. just wrtie 07 D: 07 H: 46 M: 57 S, It is still not till the edge of the screen on left and right? the content is eprfect the background colour should cover the full width of the screen right? any screen. 
